Invocation Name: taint radio
des:
taintradio was established in 2008 as a non-commercial, listener-funded venue for independent music-focused program producers. We provide an eclectic 24/7 stream of music and music-related programming. In 2011 JazzWeek named us Internet Station of the Year.
taintradio does not do on-air fundraising nor do we contact listeners asking for financial support. There is a tip jar, to which we hope you will choose to contribute.
Thank you.
